{"tid":1694461,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[議案大比例通過] 建制派要求全體公務員 必須宣誓擁護效忠特區政府","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T11:44:50.000Z","uid":270124,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b402fac1fdb4ce88c1913779af4c8ef43fda7833","tid":1694461,"uid":270124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"香港立法會公務員及資助機構員工事務委員會會議上，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，提出無約束力造成，促使請特區行政長官根據基本法第48條第4款發出行政指令，要求所有特區政府公務員宣誓擁護基本法，效忠特區政府，該最終最終獲大比例通過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mpic.haiwainet.cn/thumb/d/uploadfile/20191105/1572911947702033,w_480.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmpic.haiwainet.cn%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fuploadfile%2F20191105%2F1572911947702033%2Cw_480.png&h=cc131349&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1395caf1c7195f56ad5a26b0d33c1ed8e0b0c819","tid":1694461,"uid":270124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:29:54.000Z","msg":"香港近期發生&ldquo;公務員涉暴&rdquo;事件，令人痛心。葉劉淑儀提出動議，要求所有公務員（包括新入職公務員），宣誓擁護基本法，以及效忠中華人民共和國香港特別行政區，最終議案獲大比例通過。"},{"pid":"89acd5264d986c481cbf0848c0d1310b2c844234","tid":1694461,"uid":270124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀會後在社交媒體發文稱，特區政府作為雇主，應該對其僱員有一定要求，公務員既然有志加入特區政府就應該擁護基本法，效忠中華人民共和國香港特別行政區。帖文中指出，&ldquo;反修例&rdquo;風波已經拖了近5個月，不同群體、不同政見者之間的仇恨不斷加深，社會對立，實在危險。她直言，很多市民表示十分擔憂事態發展，擔心賠了經濟更賠了香港。"},{"pid":"329620cf6195893e446c1bb90a745c0bdc3a5c75","tid":1694461,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"想參加罷工，但又驚冇左份工？<br />\n輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZwcWhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZwcWhx.jpg&h=f252a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長期罷工效果<br />\n來同行，齊參與<br />\n返shift，射波<br />\n<br />\n邊日<span style=\"color: red;\">放假</span>/<span style=\"color: red;\">射波</span> 就好去遊客旺區振興經濟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊輪住嚟射波<br />\n入嚟集思廣益啦！<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=f74c7eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE66GT2NXnPQ_tqDaA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=dfa95c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MDhDR1TfFQfRVTi3299YuQ</a><br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦"},{"pid":"d327072b8da7bfcfebe60ca37fbfb028a645e727","tid":1694461,"uid":270124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"香港特區公務員事務局局長羅智光也表示，特區政府對公務員違法零容忍，將依法跟進被捕公務員個案。他感謝香港公務員在過去數月的艱難時刻，努力謹守崗位，應對不穩定情況，在嚴峻挑戰下，竭力服務市民，表現專業。他同時感謝警隊在最前線承受無比壓力，維持社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mpic.haiwainet.cn/thumb/d/uploadfile/20191105/1572911836613682,w_480.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmpic.haiwainet.cn%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fuploadfile%2F20191105%2F1572911836613682%2Cw_480.png&h=78c71901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅智光稱，公務員以和平方式表達個人意見，參與合法公眾活動一向是容許的。而對於有公務員在暴亂中被捕，羅智光說，每一個個案都由所屬部門跟進，他相信大家都會努力止暴制亂，讓社會盡快回復平和。"},{"pid":"95a8c0c463ef1f7c707ec26a9852aaafec875a14","tid":1694461,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"公樸關係打破,成立新政府指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4081e3da631fecaea4367521c54b3de65f4f62f8","tid":1694461,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br 